    <item>
      <title>默克尔给德国大选领跑者梅尔茨带来惊人打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/merkel-delivers-shock-german-election-blow-to-frontrunner-merz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总理安格拉·默克尔介入了德国备受争议的竞选活动，批评基督教民主党议员弗里德里希·梅尔茨决定借助极右翼势力的投票，在议会强行通过一项强硬的移民决议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/merkel-delivers-shock-german-election-blow-to-frontrunner-merz</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 10:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典寻求快速出台新法律打击黑帮爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/sweden-seeks-to-fast-track-new-law-to-tackle-gangland-bombings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典希望提出一项新法律，允许当局秘密窃听 15 岁以下儿童，因为这个北欧国家正在努力应对一系列与犯罪团伙有关的爆炸事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/sweden-seeks-to-fast-track-new-law-to-tackle-gangland-bombings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 10:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前南非总统祖马之女因制造致命骚乱被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ex-south-african-leader-zuma-s-daughter-charged-for-deadly-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非检察官以煽动恐怖主义罪起诉前南非总统雅各布·祖马的女儿，指控她参与了导致 354 人死亡的反政府骚乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ex-south-african-leader-zuma-s-daughter-charged-for-deadly-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 10:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯希望在 2029 年前完成希思罗机场项目的“开工建设”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/reeves-wants-spades-in-ground-on-heathrow-runway-before-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，她希望在 2029 年下次选举之前开始修建希思罗机场的第三条跑道。此前一天，里夫斯批准了一项引起争议的项目，该项目导致她所在的执政党工党出现分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/reeves-wants-spades-in-ground-on-heathrow-runway-before-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国大选领跑者转投德国选择党 竞选形势严峻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/german-election-front-runner-jolts-race-with-pivot-toward-afd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党总理候选人弗里德里希·梅尔茨 (Friedrich Merz) 领导的执政联盟在民意调查中以两位数领先，但在周三的竞选活动中，他却接受了民族主义政党德国选择党 (Affordable Alternative) 的投票，同意在议会通过一项强硬的移民决议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/german-election-front-runner-jolts-race-with-pivot-toward-afd</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 09:05:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管特朗普下达援助令，乌干达仍向艾滋病患者保证提供医疗服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/uganda-reassures-hiv-patients-of-care-despite-trump-s-aid-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌干达试图消除艾滋病患者对美国援助冻结将中断治疗的担忧，并承诺将继续开展此类项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/uganda-reassures-hiv-patients-of-care-despite-trump-s-aid-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 08:47:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨和卡加梅就卢旺达支持刚果围攻事件互相指责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ramaphosa-kagame-trade-barbs-over-rwanda-backed-siege-in-congo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅指责南非总统对刚果民主共和国东部冲突的评论“撒谎”和“歪曲”，这在该地区争取停火的努力中加剧了两位领导人之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/ramaphosa-kagame-trade-barbs-over-rwanda-backed-siege-in-congo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 08:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯寻求与特朗普举行会谈讨论移民和国防问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/philippines-marcos-seeks-trump-meeting-to-discuss-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯表示，他希望与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普会面，讨论国防和贸易关系以及面临被驱逐出境风险的数千名菲律宾人的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/philippines-marcos-seeks-trump-meeting-to-discuss-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 07:54:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治混乱动摇主要经济体 欧元区未能实现增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/french-economy-shrinks-as-political-mayhem-erodes-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧元区两大经济体政府倒台，企业和消费者信心受挫，欧元区经济去年年底意外陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/french-economy-shrinks-as-political-mayhem-erodes-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
